title: Was the child born alive in 23 weeks "sucking in the garbage"?
subtitle: In September 2019, life-supporters highlighted the Florida case in 2006 in Sycloria Williams.
author: Dan MacGuill
vclaim: In 2006, the owner of the abortion clinic cut off the rope of a child born alive before "throwing it" into a biologically dangerous bag and placed its remains in the garbage.
